{"tid":2199732,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[Excel撚] 有冇好嘅Excel學習網?","createTime":"2020-09-12T12:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T13:20:45.000Z","uid":171094,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8597d23012c735956131c00fc44ce53c377a0b5f","tid":2199732,"uid":171094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T12:12:13.000Z","msg":"做咗幾年嘢都會成日都用到excel <br />\n但好多時都係解決唔到一個問題先至上網搵解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到晒咗好多時間喺度trial and error<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得自己效率仲可以提高好多<br />\n所以決心學好一套excel concepts<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以後遇到問題就可以自己諗方法唔使成日查<br />\n但呢排又唔係好想出去上堂   仲做緊肺炎恐懼撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴絲有好嘅網可以學Excel? 最好有埋sample可以down落嚟自己試<br />\n感激 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7468d40e2792302686f02fe2d7c5767ff50775c","tid":2199732,"uid":13791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T12:13:33.000Z","msg":"完全唔識用excel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd人係咪讀u時專登去學?"},{"pid":"a948288e4746bc6e86a7dcef814291b5dfc1ca3e","tid":2199732,"uid":171094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7468d40e2792302686f02fe2d7c5767ff50775c","tid":2199732,"uid":13791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T12:13:33.000Z","msg":"完全唔識用excel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd人係咪讀u時專登去學?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T12:17:47.000Z","msg":"我本身係soc sci撚<br />\n讀u嗰陣成日要用spss計嘢<br />\n但因為spss都學唔好<br />\n有時就上網查吓excel有冇得gen到一啲圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就慢慢學咗小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都想知係咪個個會出去俾錢學<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a63658efd9066824934f4ab0d9c6c80f2554567","tid":2199732